quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  26,176,Kaom Aikah pih peusulet Rasul Han jitem kaboi peue nyang geupeugah
  26,177,Geukheun le Syuʻib ubak awak nyan Pakon gata han takwa keu Allah
  26,178,Lon nyoe bit Rasul jeuet tapeucaya
  26,179,Teuma takwa gata keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
  26,180,Hana bak gata lon lakee upah Upah lon ka na bak Po dum alam
  26,181,Teuma sukatan bek tapeusalah Beu santeut are ‘oh tabloe peubloe Bek tapeurugoe dum hamba Allah
  26,182,Ngon ceng nyang beutoi watee tatimang Bek miyup manyang on ceng dua blah
  26,183,Barang-barang gop bek tapeukureueng Buet nyan that hareuem beu tapeusiblah Bek peubuet jeuheut di dalam bumoe
  26,184,Takwa jinoe laju keu Allah Tuhan nyang peujeuet gata nyoe bandum Angkatan jameun pih hana ubah Ureueng nyang dilee pih Tuhan peujeuet
  26,185,Jiseuot leugat peue roe tapeugah Ka jipeusihe gata uroe nyoe
  26,186,Gata ngon kamoe kon saban leupah Gata ngon kamoe sit manusia Meukira gata sang sulet leupah
  26,187,Peurhot bak kamoe geureupeng langet Meu beuna keubit peue nyang tapeugah
  26,188,Geukheun Tuhan lon bandum Neuteupeue Buetteuh beurangpeue Neuteupeue sudah
  26,189,Jikheun treuk sulet Syuʻib Rasul jih Geuazeueb treuk jih nyang brat sileupah Uroe meuawan uroe kiamat Haro hara that hana ban peugah
  26,190,Atra nyan bandum pih jeuet keu tanda € Allah Taʻala kuasa leupah Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Hana atra nyan jitueng phaedah
  26,191,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah